    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，成功和失败两个分支都连到Done了。我检查一下整体结构，起点是Start System Update，终点是Done。",
      "elements_involved": [
